OL,3,CMore than half of schools face cuts
OL,4,Camid huge budget deficits
OL,6,FMore than half of schools say they
OL,7,Fface a budget deficit which is forcing
OL,8,Fthem to make cuts to staff numbers and
OL,9,Fthe services they provide, according
OL,10,Fto headteachers.
OL,12,FThe National Association of
OL,13,FHeadteachers' report says more than
OL,14,F27% of school leaders face financial
OL,15,Fpressures for the first time this year.
OL,17,FIt says teachers are becoming
OL,18,Fincreasingly concerned that without
OL,19,Fextra funding, they will be unable to
OL,20,F"meet the needs of all their pupils
OL,21,Ffully."
