OL,3,CMore than half of schools face cuts
OL,4,Camid huge budget deficits
OL,6,FThe latest figures show the number of
OL,7,Fheadteachers with concerns about their
OL,8,Fbudget has nearly doubled in just one
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThe report blames inflation,
OL,12,Fincreasing wages, cover staff and
OL,13,Flocal funding formulae for the huge
OL,14,Fshortfalls some schools are
OL,15,Fexperiencing.
