OL,3,CMore than half of schools face cuts
OL,4,Camid huge budget deficits
OL,6,FChris Parry, president of NAHT Cymru
OL,7,Fsaid: "School leaders are caught
OL,8,Fbetween a rock and a hard place, being
OL,9,Fforced to cut staff, reduce support
OL,10,Fservices, and compromise essential
OL,11,Flearning resources simply to stay
OL,12,Fafloat.
