OL,3,CMore than half of schools face cuts
OL,4,Camid huge budget deficits
OL,6,F"These findings should serve as a wake-
OL,7,Fup call for the Welsh Government about
OL,8,Fthe need for immediate action. The
OL,9,Ffunding crisis threatens the quality
OL,10,Fof education, and without a clear,
OL,11,Fstrategic response, schools will be
OL,12,Funable to provide the support that
OL,13,Fpupils and staff need. A long-term
OL,14,Fsolution is essential."
OL,16,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said,
OL,17,F"The amount of funding set aside for
OL,18,Fschool budgets, including funding for
OL,19,Fschool staff, is for local authorities
OL,20,Fto determine, we do not fund schools
OL,21,Fdirectly.
